    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/fdda36f23e76d52d13686c78c2e8f7f7.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=600 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/fdda36f23e76d52d13686c78c2e8f7f7.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/fdda36f23e76d52d13686c78c2e8f7f7.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>UnSafe </strong> 是一款最多 4 人游玩的合作恐怖生存游戏。你和你的队员从“黑色巨石” 空间站的冷冻状态中苏醒。虽然是你们设置了空间站的设备和装置，但你们不知道接下来发生了什么。你最终的苏醒意味着一件事：一切都出了问题。调查该区域，详细了解在你沉睡时都发生了什么。绕过安保系统，收集数据，面对危险。保持团结。保持理智。活下去。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/9d28813c2b7e22f53b78d4c181cae268.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=800 height=230 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/9d28813c2b7e22f53b78d4c181cae268.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/9d28813c2b7e22f53b78d4c181cae268.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Trello Roadmap: <br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>多人游戏</strong>：组建一个最多 4 人的小组，探索荒废的空间站。合作绕过计算机安保系统，逃离危险，或救回倒下的战友。<br><br></li><li><strong>通讯</strong>：使用你的麦克风与队友沟通。如果远离团队，那么只有沉寂与你为伍。<br><br></li><li><strong>游戏性</strong>：在太空中的恐怖体验。类似“异形”（电影）的氛围，玩家在虚空的恐怖面前无能为力，但并非毫无希望。 <br><br></li><li><strong>地图</strong>：探索废弃的两层空间站。每一个转角似乎都很熟悉，但这对你有利吗？<br><br></li><li><strong>环境</strong>：逼真的图形和声音营造了一种幽闭恐惧的气氛。最小化的用户界面增加了被遗弃在太空中的感觉。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/76ccd6d43d58a8dc0b63081942925b4c.poster.avif?t=1763472714\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/76ccd6d43d58a8dc0b63081942925b4c.webm?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1756160/extras/76ccd6d43d58a8dc0b63081942925b4c.mp4?t=1763472714\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
